## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="8a346-109"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> 如果存在环境事务，并且 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A> 调用了事务并随后进行了回滚，则可能会停止响应。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a346-109"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> may stop responding when there is an ambient transaction and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A> is called and afterwards the transaction is rolled back.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a346-110">如果在 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> 事务回滚完成之前调用，则会存在争用条件，导致调用 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> 停止响应。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a346-110">If <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> is called prior to the transaction rollback completing, a race condition will exist, causing the call to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> to stop responding.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a346-111">下面的伪代码示例对此进行了说明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a346-111">This can be illustrated by the following pseudo-code example</span></span>  
  
```  
using (TransactionScope ts = new TransactionScope())   
{  
   try  
   {  
       rc.Complete();  
      ...  
   }  
   Catch (Exception)   
   {  
      rc.Abandon()  
   }  
}  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8a346-112">这不是建议使用的模式 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a346-112">This is not the recommended pattern for working with <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a346-113">应将 try/catch 块放在事务范围之外。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a346-113">Instead the try/catch block should be placed outside of the transaction scope.</span></span>

